Implementation complete. 40 tests pass covering all rules and examples from the spec — base premiums, component blocks (exactly-3 rule), item-specific modifiers (curse/high enchantment), customer modifiers (loyalty/first insurance/follow-up), modifier scope on multi-item policies, rounding in MHPCO's favor, claim payouts (deductible, high-enchantment, dragon material, dragon+high-ench tie-breaker), cap exhaustion across multiple claims, multiple items of same type, and error cases (unknown type, missing item, negative damage). CLI at `src/cli.ts` reads JSON from stdin and writes results to stdout, exiting non-zero on errors.
